    com.yworks.yfiles.layout.tree

  • Classes in com.yworks.yfiles.layout.tree used by com.yworks.yfiles.layout.circular

    BalloonLayout
    A tree layout algorithm that arranges the subtrees of the tree in a balloon-like fashion.
